    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行行长潘功胜表示，中国政策重点将更多地转向消费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/china-policy-focus-to-shift-more-to-consumption-pboc-s-pan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行行长表示，中国将提升消费在经济中的作用，摆脱单纯依赖投资的模式，从而实现过去 20 年来决定中国经济命运的增长模式的转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/china-policy-focus-to-shift-more-to-consumption-pboc-s-pan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 04:21:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯液化天然气货物运抵西班牙附近，测试最新制裁的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/russian-lng-cargo-near-spain-to-test-impact-of-latest-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，一艘装载着俄罗斯一家工厂货物的液化天然气油轮即将首次考验买家规避最新一轮惩罚措施的意愿。俄罗斯一家工厂受到华盛顿的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/russian-lng-cargo-near-spain-to-test-impact-of-latest-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 04:10:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：亚洲股市下跌，油价因俄罗斯制裁上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/asian-stocks-under-pressure-after-blowout-us-jobs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，美国公布的就业数据强于预期，导致亚洲股市和债市下跌，而美国对俄罗斯实施新一轮制裁可能导致石油供应减少，导致油价攀升至四个月高位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/asian-stocks-under-pressure-after-blowout-us-jobs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 22:26:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
